Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.35,TXT CN,,0,0,0,,钱包不见了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.20,TXT JP,,0,0,0,,ママー
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.20,TXT CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.20,TXT JP,,0,0,0,,落ちてたわよ～
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.20,TXT CN,,0,0,0,,掉在这里了呦～
